HEADWORD: Mayflower
<hw>May"flow`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>In England, the hawthorn; in New England, the trailing arbutus (see
<er>Arbutus</er>); also, the blossom of these plants.</def>⟦br⟧
